QuestData.Title: Bloodied Blades of Zeth'Gol
QuestData.Description: Them Bleeding Hollow orcs do blood magic - like voodoo but it hurt more. They cut their own flesh. Most of 'em carry curved ritual blades for carvin' themselves up.$b$bBring me them blades, commander. We can turn their power against 'em.
QuestData.LogDescription: Collect $oa Bleeding Hollow Ritual Blades from Bleeding Hollow orcs in Zeth'Gol.
